## Structured output

```python
from pydantic import BaseModel

class Plan(BaseModel):
    intent: str
    steps: list[str]

agent = BaseAgent(name="planner", instructions="...", output_schema=Plan)
resp = await runner.run(agent, "...")
plan: Plan = resp.structured_output
```

